{"tid":348801,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"(請大神指教)keyboard同touch pad冇反應","createTime":"2017-08-06T04:46:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T06:53:37.000Z","uid":42128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"757ae60be5e1d24c2ed32ed7f5d3f5047bdc6fb4","tid":348801,"uid":42128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T04:46:54.000Z","msg":"話說尋日上網睇睇吓直播發現部macbk air個keyboard同touch pad都冇反應,<br />\n插咗個usb mouse就ok,<br />\n咁我用mouse熄機諗住今朝開番機可能冇事,<br />\n點知今朝開番都係咁,<br />\nkick住喺login度,<br />\nkeyboard用唔到打唔到pw,<br />\n又搵唔到螢幕鍵盤,<br />\n部機依家好似run片run得慢咁沙沙聲好嘈,<br />\n但又唔會發熱架喎.<br />\n有冇巴絲試過咁樣?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb3265372186a0c249995b08c4400c602ac3911","tid":348801,"uid":62734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:10:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說尋日上網睇睇吓直播發現部macbk air個keyboard同touch pad都冇反應,<br />\n插咗個usb mouse就ok,<br />\n咁我用mouse熄機諗住今朝開番機可能冇事,<br />\n點知今朝開番都係咁,<br />\nkick住喺login度,<br />\nkeyboard用唔到打唔到pw,<br />\n又搵唔到螢幕鍵盤,<br />\n部機依家好似run片run得慢咁沙沙聲好嘈,<br />\n但又唔會發熱架喎.<br />\n有冇巴絲試過咁樣?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n插個 keyboard 落去囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd715e3432ee603fc4ef16fb885c63a3f52c1e7","tid":348801,"uid":6677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:13:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT201295\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-us%2FHT201295&d=RXwih5i%2FRi3UFcgrGh8mwQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=160bbce0\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT201295</a>"},{"pid":"dee4c6d3a2617da76c858c6ae02bb67470d8153d","tid":348801,"uid":42128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:30:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT201295\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupp